### **Please note that the abstract deadline submission date is Thursday, 21
The Conference Organising Committee will meet in February 2021 to decide which
abstracts will be accepted for presentation at the 2021 conference; authors
will be informed of their abstract outcome by the end of February 2021.
Authors who have not received confirmation by the end of February should
contact Rob Glyn Jones at Hg3 Conferences, telephone: +44 (0) 1423 529333 or
(PDF, 1.1MB) and **example abstracts** (PDF, 205KB) are available to support
There are eight awards that abstracts may be eligible for.
Abstracts will be automatically entered in the following award(s) using the
'Award Criteria' section of the submission form. Abstracts can be considered
for more than one award as long as they are eligible for entry.
All eligible abstracts will be anonymously reviewed by a panel of markers
invited by the Diabetes UK Professional Conference Organising Committee for
shortlisting. A panel of judges invited by the committee will judge the
Shortlisted oral presentations will be judged at the specific oral session for
Arrangements for poster award judging are to be confirmed.
